# ============================================================================
# NOTES:
# 
# 1. This .gitignore is configured for:
#    - Python projects
#    - Machine Learning models
#    - Audio processing applications
#    - Multi-platform development (Windows, Mac, Linux)
# 
# 2. To add exceptions (files you want to track):
#    !path/to/file.txt
# 
# 3. To ignore entire directories but keep structure:
#    directory/*
#    !directory/.gitkeep
# 
# 4. Large files:
#    - Consider using Git LFS for models > 100MB
#    - Store on cloud storage (S3, Azure Blob) and document in README
# 
# 5. Sensitive data:
#    - NEVER commit API keys, passwords, or credentials
#    - Use environment variables or secret management services
#    - Scan with tools like git-secrets or truffleHog
# ============================================================================
